data.description: Come see the new updates made to this meticulously maintained 3 bed 2 bath split floor plan home. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room with a wood-burning fireplace. The open concept design allows the kitchen to overlook the living room, perfect for everyday living and entertaining guests. This home boasts a desirable split-bedroom floor plan. The master bedroom is generously sized and includes an ensuite bathroom with separate sinks, a luxurious soaking tub and a separate shower. Two separate his and her walk-in closets in the master bedroom offer ample storage space. Two additional bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home which share a well-appointed full bathroom. Step outside to the covered patio, where you can enjoy outdoor meals, entertain guests, or simply relax in the shade. This home offers ample storage including oversized closets, garage storage and a walk in pantry. Roof replaced 2022, AC replaced 2019, Fresh paint Behr-Blank Canvas.
